      "info": {
        "contact": {
          "name": "support@bluefin.com"
        },
        "description": "This page describes the Bluefin Partner Application Programming Interface (API) for the Decryptx service. This service allows partners to decrypt PCI-validated Point-To-Point Encryption (P2PE) card information.\n\n<strong>IP Address Whitelist</strong><br/>\nAt Bluefin, we protect our REST endpoints with a IP address whitelist. If you would like to try the examples below please <a href=\"https://www.bluefin.com/contact/\">contact us</a> to request access.\n\n# Authentication\nAll API calls to the Decryptx APIs require authentication; our endpoints support Transparent, Basic, Digest, HMAC, and RSA authentication methods. To explore our authentication methods check out our Authentication documentation.\n",
        "license": {
          "name": "Bluefin Software Licence"
        },
